 while longer and cracked a few more jokes, and the interview was concluded with advice for students.<\/p>\n<p>\u201cYou have built a foundation at Northwest, your teachers prepare you&#8230;for advice I would just say do the little things. Humility, helping others in a time of need, the little things make a big difference. Doing the right thing when nobody is lookin<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Northwest Principal Gil Alvarez spoke at a recent Fellowship of Christian Athletes (FCA) meeting at Pathways Church to discuss values, respect and the attitude presented at Northwest. Alvarez opened his speech by saying that when he was younger he had been both president and vice president of his FCA when he was younger and was&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[459,4],"tags":[167],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2565"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2565"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2565\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2567,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2565\/revisions\/2567"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2565"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2565"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":